metadata.name: Beg The Sun
metadata.description:
Title: Beg The Sun
Date: October, 2018
Location: Chumphon, Thailand
.
2018 was hard for me.
When you lose someone you love, 
When your heart is turning blue.
I look outside of the windows.
I beg the sun to give me warmth.
I beg the sun to keep me strong.
And here I am, still and strong.
.
CVAS (1/5)
